 March. The <span style=\"color: red;\">Easter Term</span> shall begin on 10 April and shall consist of seventy days ending on 18 June, provided that in any year in which full Easter Term begins on or after 22 April the Easter Term shall begin on 17 April and end on 25 June."},{"pid":"cae3245f99995d8718576dc08aa3055093f8dd03","tid":237771,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFrom the Statutes and Ordinances of the University of Cambridge<br />\n<br />\nThe <span style=\"color: red;\">Michaelmas Term</span> shall begin on 1 October and shall consist of eighty days, ending on 19 December. The <span style=\"color: red;\">Lent Term</span> shall begin on 5 January and shall consist of eighty days, ending on 25 March or in any leap year on 24 March. The <span style=\"color: red;\">Easter Term</span> shall begin on 10 April and shall consist of seventy days ending on 18 June, provided that in any year in which full Easter Term begins on or after 22 April the Easter Term shall begin on 17 April and end on 25 June.</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來係Scotland先用semester"},{"pid":"e28e5004413560670e1688e25b0b38b01d9052c2","tid":237771,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T20:19:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我地英美都熱愛 即係唔鐘意中國</blockquote><br />\n只係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我地英美都熱愛 只係唔鐘意中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb02feb579b38d7de0b9b89a57c50d5916f546f5","tid":237771,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T02:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我地英美都熱愛 即係唔鐘意中國</blockquote><br />\n只係</blockquote><br />\n我地英美都熱愛 只係唔鐘意中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到英式口音好高尚美式係垃圾但自己又卷